GREAT LAKES DREDGE & DOCK COMPANY v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 45623] [104 C. Cls. 818;

328 U. S. —]

Government contract; deductions made by defendant for overdepth dredging. Petition dismissed. .

Plaintiff’s petition for writ of certiorari denied by the ' Supreme Court May 27, 1946.
